Class Exercise

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Exercise
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExerciseAerobic, ExerciseStrength

    public abstract class Exercise
extends java.lang.Object
    This is an abstract that acts as the parent class for ExerciseAerobic and ExerciseStrength. It contains fields and method that will pertain to all things dealing with student exercises.
